des:
Ask for Motivate Me, and energise yourself.

Feeling downside? become a better human by listening to powerful motivation tonic.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Motivate Me" or "Alexa, open Motivate Me" to get a motivation phrase".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
